											<a href="https://www.insidehook.com/article/television/gordon-ramsay-tv-empire-masterchef-hells-kitchen?utm_source=direct&#038;utm_medium=inline&#038;utm_campaign=related" class="align-middle">
										A Beginner&#039;s Guide to Gordon Ramsay&#039;s Sprawling, Tyrannical TV Empire</a>
